{
  "stem": "521.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "OK, that's-- what did I do with it?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So anyway, then my-- my-- my fiancee was writing a regular letter and said, we won't be able to send you any more letters.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is our last letter-- letter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she admonishes me that I should look after myself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Of course, I was looking after myself as much as I could.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And at that time, she was still believing in God.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she hoped that God is going to help me and-- and said I shouldn't despair-- writes about-- about God, who was just about ready to kill them-- killed-- killed her parents and my parents.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So it's a good advice what I have received from her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And admonishes me that I should watch out for myself seemingly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She didn't really think that God is going to help me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she sends me kisses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she loves me forever.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now, it's beautiful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Of course, God didn't help me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And God didn't help her and my parents either.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "God was on the other side.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So what happens is before all this, we have-- as I told you, we were crossing over to Poland.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But before we have crossed over, or the officer who was in charge, was stopping us on the-- on the border as Jews.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we had to sing the Hungarian hymn and then some other patriotic songs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then we stepped out of Hungary into Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "How did you travel?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were walking all the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were walking up the Carpathians.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And on the other side, we were walking down the Carpathians.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I forgot to tell you that at that time, the food became scarce.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as we were helping those horse-drawn carts, one of the horses broke his leg or something happened.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was destroyed.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
